c_n = \frac{1}{2\pi} \int_{-\pi}^{\pi} \sum_{k = 1}^{\infty} \frac{e^{i(k - n)x}}{2^k} dx = \frac{1}{2\pi} \frac{2\pi}{2^n} = \frac{1}{2^n}
\int_{-\pi}^{\pi} |g(x)|^2 dx = 2\pi \sum\limits_{n = 1}^{\infty} |c_n|^2 = 2\pi \sum_{n = 1}^{\infty} 4^{-n} = \frac{2\pi}{3}
